ates\nfor dynamically induced TTV variations. Conclusions. Those systems with\nperiodic TTVs that we cannot explain with systematics from observation, stellar\nrotation, activity, or inadequate sampling may be multiple systems or even\nexomoon hosts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2012 12:53:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Jan 2013 15:55:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Mar 2013 21:41:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
